49:39.498 --> 49:43.545
 Happy birthday to you

49:45.243 --> 49:46.809
- Whoo!

49:46.853 --> 49:48.507
- It's not my birthday.

49:50.074 --> 49:52.206
Did I get the day wrong?

49:52.250 --> 49:55.035
- You got the season wrong.
- Oh, dear.

49:55.079 --> 49:58.299
- Ugh, I'm thinking about
her sister's birthday.

49:58.343 --> 49:59.997
- Nope.
Not even close.

50:03.391 --> 50:05.828
- Well, somebody's birthday,
right?

50:05.872 --> 50:08.222
- Wait, is this--

50:08.266 --> 50:11.225
this is why you two were
chatting outside together?

50:11.269 --> 50:12.313
My God.
Mom.

50:16.535 --> 50:19.233
You know, let's get some forks
and some plates.

50:19.277 --> 50:21.235
We're not letting good cake
go to waste.

50:21.279 --> 50:22.280
- Some forks and plates,
people.

50:22.323 --> 50:24.412
- Yes.

50:40.167 --> 50:42.343
- You are right on time.

50:42.387 --> 50:43.518
- I'm always on time.

50:43.562 --> 50:45.607
- Walk around this way.

50:50.438 --> 50:53.833
- This is nice.
Just the two of us.

50:53.876 --> 50:55.574
Although today,
Bobbi said she missed you.

50:55.617 --> 50:57.184
- Did she?

50:57.228 --> 50:58.881
- Well, technically,
she said, "I miss mass,"

50:58.925 --> 51:00.535
but she's not Catholic,
so...

51:00.579 --> 51:02.537
I'm just assuming
she meant you.

51:02.581 --> 51:05.105
-  I know they're not mine

51:05.149 --> 51:06.846
- Is everything okay?

51:06.889 --> 51:09.501
- Just thinking about
our "perfect family."

51:09.544 --> 51:11.894
I know, that was so awkward.

51:11.938 --> 51:14.549
- I don't know about you,

51:14.593 --> 51:17.552
but I feel so far from perfect.

51:17.596 --> 51:19.206
- Well, yeah, plus the part

51:19.250 --> 51:21.121
where we're
not actually a family.

51:21.165 --> 51:22.470
- I think that's the problem.

51:22.514 --> 51:26.866
I mean, Bobbi and Luna
think we are family.

51:26.909 --> 51:30.130
-  Don't be so caught up

51:30.174 --> 51:32.611
- And why wouldn't they?

51:32.654 --> 51:34.526
It was all pretend.

51:34.569 --> 51:36.484
- I really liked pretending.

51:36.528 --> 51:39.618
-  I see problems
down the line 

51:39.661 --> 51:42.229
- Me too.

51:42.273 --> 51:45.276
I like pretending,
that I'm not...

51:45.319 --> 51:46.668
Still grieving.

51:46.712 --> 51:50.890
I like pretending
that Luna has a mom.

51:53.501 --> 51:55.460
And I think we know
we're pretending, but...

51:57.505 --> 51:58.680
But they don't.

52:03.424 --> 52:05.165
- It's not fair, is it?

52:06.514 --> 52:09.561
-  But there was a dirt
upon your hands 

52:09.604 --> 52:13.173
- I wish I met you
in a few years.

52:13.217 --> 52:15.523
Then maybe...

52:18.700 --> 52:23.444
- I had so much fun.

52:24.967 --> 52:27.448
And I didn't think
I could anymore.

52:31.539 --> 52:33.367
-  I see problems
down the line 

52:34.977 --> 52:36.457
I should go.

52:36.501 --> 52:38.720
-  I know that I'm right

52:42.246 --> 52:43.638
- Okay.

52:45.249 --> 52:46.641
-  Don't let the darkness
eat you up 

